<% frontend_host = ENV.fetch("FRONTEND_URL", "http://localhost:3101") %>
<% invitation_url = "#{frontend_host}/auth/accept-invitation?invitation_token=#{@token}" %>
You're invited to join AQVC Hub!

Hi <%= @resource.first_name %>,

<% if @resource.invited_by %><%= @resource.invited_by.first_name %> <%= @resource.invited_by.last_name %> has invited you to join AQVC Hub.<% else %>You've been invited to join AQVC Hub.<% end %> Visit the link below to set up your account:

<%= invitation_url %>

This invitation will expire in <%= distance_of_time_in_words(User.invite_for) %>. If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.

<%= Date.current.year %> AQVC Hub. All rights reserved.
